    Description
    AbstractEventMapData
    Abstract base class for managing a map of events, where each event is associated with a unique identifier (String).
    CollisionData
    A concrete implementation of AbstractEventMapData for handling collision events.
    CustomEventData
    A concrete implementation of AbstractEventMapData for handling custom, user-made events.
    EditorEvent
    Represents an event associated with an editor object, encapsulating its conditions, outcomes, and corresponding parameter mappings.
    EventData
    The EventData class holds a list of all events by string ID in a specific order.
    ExecutorData
    A class representing a singular exeuctor (condition/outcome) for an event.
    InputData
    A concrete implementation of AbstractEventMapData for handling input events.

    A concrete implementation of AbstractEventMapData for handling physics events.
